query:
/*+ NoNestLoop(i ss dd) */ select i.i_brand_id AS brand_id,
i.i_brand AS brand,
sum(ss.ss_ext_sales_price) AS ext_price
from item AS i
inner join store_sales AS ss
on ss.ss_item_sk = i.i_item_sk AND i.i_manager_id = 77
inner join date_dim AS dd
on dd.d_date_sk = ss.ss_sold_date_sk AND dd.d_moy = 12 AND dd.d_year = 2002 group by i.i_brand, i.i_brand_id order by ext_price desc, i.i_brand_id LIMIT 100;
